<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT1.9">
<l>tuttaṅ kaikkiḷḷai viḷari tāra muḻaiyiḷi yōcaipaṇ keḻumap pāṭic</l>
<l>caccari kokkarai takkai yōṭu takuṇitan tuntupi tāḷam vīṇai</l>
<l>mattaḷaṅ karaṭikai vaṉkai meṉṟōṟ ṟamarukaṅ kuṭamuḻā montai vācit</l>
<l>tattaṉai viraviṉō ṭāṭu meṅka ḷappa ṉiṭamtiru vālaṅ kāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where our father dances with a mixture of so much</l>
<l>playing the Caccari, the Kokkarai, along with the Takkai drum the Takuṇitam drum,</l>
<l>the Tuntupi drum, the cymbals, the lute, the Mattaḷam drum, the Karaṭikai drum, the Vaṉkai drum,</l>
<l>the soft-skinned kettle drum, the Kuṭamuḻā drum [and] the Montai drum, singing jointly the melody</l>
<l>on the sound of the second, the third, the sixth seventh, fourth [and] fifth note, is Tiruvalaṅkāṭu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
